    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## VAPT A2 — Generate Proposal\n\n**Trigger:** Sub-workflow dipanggil oleh Bot A Dispatcher (`/generate_proposal`)\n\n**Flow (4 langkah via Redis session):**\n1. Masukkan nama klien/perusahaan\n2. Masukkan daftar objek pengujian\n3. Pilih metodologi (Black/Grey/White Box) — inline keyboard\n4. Deskripsikan ruang lingkup\n   → Fetch template proposal dari Notion (`NOTION_PAGE_PROPOSAL_TEMPLATE`)\n   → Claude generate proposal mengikuti struktur template\n\n**Output:** Proposal VAPT 10 bagian dalam Bahasa Indonesia dikirim ke PM via Bot A\n\n**Template:** Halaman Notion dengan konten template sebagai rich text blocks\n**Session Key:** `vapt:session:{chatId}` (TTL 1 jam)",
        "height": 250,
        "width": 510
      },
      "id": "e5000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000020",
      "name": "Sticky Note - Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        -300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "block",
        "operation": "getAll",
        "blockId": "={{ $vars.NOTION_PAGE_PROPOSAL_TEMPLATE }}",
        "returnAll": true
      },
      "id": "e5000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000021",
      "name": "Fetch Proposal Template",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.notion",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        750,
        450
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "notionApi": {
          "id": "{{ NOTION_CRED }}",
          "name": "Notion API"
        }
      },
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000,
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "runOnceForAllItems",
        "jsCode": "const blocks = $input.all().map(i => i.json);\nconst sessionItem = $('Parse Session Step').first().json;\n\nconst textTypes = ['paragraph','heading_1','heading_2','heading_3',\n  'bulleted_list_item','numbered_list_item','to_do','quote','callout','code'];\n\nconst lines = blocks\n  .filter(b => textTypes.includes(b.type))\n  .map(b => {\n    const content = b[b.type];\n    if (!content?.rich_text) return '';\n    const text = content.rich_text.map(r => r.plain_text || '').join('');\n    if (!text.trim()) return '';\n    if (b.type === 'heading_1') return '\\n# ' + text;\n    if (b.type === 'heading_2') return '\\n## ' + text;\n    if (b.type === 'heading_3') return '\\n### ' + text;\n    if (b.type === 'bulleted_list_item') return '\\u2022 ' + text;\n    if (b.type === 'numbered_list_item') return '- ' + text;\n    return text;\n  })\n  .filter(t => t);\n\nconst templateText = lines.length > 0 ? lines.join('\\n') : '';\n\nreturn [{ json: {\n  templateText,\n  chatId: sessionItem.chatId,\n  step: sessionItem.step,\n  data: sessionItem.data || {},\n  text: sessionItem.text || ''\n} }];"
      },
